Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Echoing at sundown, breaking a promise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Scold me as I stand alone, my nose running
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My responses are incomprehensible; a chestnut-colored evening
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:02:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was never my intention, yet I'm again selfishly causing you trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My elderly ring slips away; I put it on for it to slip away again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to feel your warmth from your words, even as white grows in my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be lonely if I grew senile first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:03:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Food spills from my mouth, dirtying the table
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forgive me and my broad grin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My responses are incomprehensible; a snow white night
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:04:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you keep on smiling when I'm just causing you trouble?
